Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩網路遊戲必須和供應商簽約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取得帳號之後才可以玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要到哪裡簽約？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說明書最後一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有供應商的電話號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先在畫面上連到那裡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它說“因您的線路問題無法連線”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你現在正透過\N電話線路和我通電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我一邊看說明書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊想辦法試試看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還得花不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個授權費是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個月要一千元？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，第一個月是免費的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寬頻接頭是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼錯誤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他睡得這麼正大光明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼又錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是網路設定\N你自己搞定好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，就算看說明書我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（連線成功）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經連上線了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟秀樹一起玩遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該一開始就去找新保幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那就馬上來開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也來一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想回去預習\N明天補習班要上的地方耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天不預習沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下，休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛，來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩，一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了，來了，來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲連表情都會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來就像是個菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲會隨著我們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變表情或動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦，是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你的角色\N那麼像清水老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臨時做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是感覺上很像而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那張臉\N配那個聲音總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，讓我們去冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為遊戲裡可以自由調整大小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的機能都會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那ちぃ怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有ちぃ不在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是連到其他伺服器了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你總算連上線了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這遊戲對於不同的城鎮\N會使用不同的伺服器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉此限制同時上線的玩家人數
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮已經客滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ可能被強制傳送到\N其他城鎮去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快去找她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的其他城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為通常有20個伺服器在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面又各分成15個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合計共有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓ちぃ孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說菜鳥真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種人來玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲會變得很難玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你千萬不要做奇怪的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你一個人的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以自由進來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣喜歡說漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在網路上很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你那個菜鳥好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路上也有那種沒禮貌的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間在這裡閒聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會找到妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以多欺少太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍對那些傢伙是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要仔細閱讀說明書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這類的遊戲你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我是第一次玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中時因為老是在照顧牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒時間玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還敢一個人獨自冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太魯莽了，太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有那麼多恐怖的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不能讓ちぃ孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是遊戲而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全一副菜鳥樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太魯莽了，太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（存檔中）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（存檔完畢）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結…結果還是沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我聽到了秀樹的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有跟秀樹在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，今天晚上再玩吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩人的膽子還真大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果今天上課又睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去\N我真的考得上學校嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好看啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啦，DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你好像沒睡飽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看到天亮啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒買片子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，這個拿回去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長，這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的秘密收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候還我都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 DVD 的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，你借了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是動作片啦，動作片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我珍藏的動作片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ大概很期待玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不能天天玩遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始要拼命讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來，秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也來玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟秀樹一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們今天也在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩才有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要跟ちぃ一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼ちぃ今天還是不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伺服器應該沒那麼多人才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為人數的關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又跑到其他的城鎮去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說如果電腦的性能太強時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會給遊戲的伺服器\N帶來很大的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候會不能玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要亂用魔法的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王終於登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼強嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看雜誌和網路上的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過有人打倒過他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險，危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過這裡就可以到下個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想不開了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不贏那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（恭喜過關）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快幫我倒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是錄影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過剛剛那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好像真的是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好厲害喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ打倒了大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ什麼都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以另一個角色的身份出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒無敵的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道ちぃ擁有\N超越伺服器等級的性能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的 CPU 就跟超級電腦同等級…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，不玩遊戲了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，因為已經破關了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且ちぃ要是又不見了\N我會很傷腦筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒辦法一起玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次再玩別的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩不必連上網路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有別的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個是店長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ，那不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我跟妳說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重考生沒有暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了讀書讀書，還是讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:23:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是海灘陽傘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,義大利是世界的陽傘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是游泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水中的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會受到其所排開的水\N相同重量的浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿，船，喘，串
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會在海邊啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，去海邊」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.28,0:24:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快樂喔
